title: Managing a 9-5 with a Freelance Career, TikTok & NYC with Alex Frank
itunes:title: Managing a 9-5 with a Freelance Career, TikTok & NYC with Alex Frank
description:
On this episode Alex Frank talks to Brooke about her journey from being a science major to now working in photography/film. Alex describes how she built up her portfolio following a career set back and shares tips to growing a TikTok audience. 

Check Out By Chari: https://bychari.com 

Thanks to Alex for coming on the show!  Check her out @shotzbyalex on Instagram and TikTok.
